Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.62,0:00:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you just have to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words\Nlured men to the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.01,0:00:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,in pursuit of dreams greater\Nthan they've ever dared
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to imagine! This is the time\Nknown as the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.43,0:00:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.03,0:01:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] To think that these\Nbrats have held you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How the Black Cat\NPirates have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE, SIAM]\NYou're not our Captain anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so we have to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha. I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tiger Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,--[snoring]\N--Get up, you bum!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami, that's my eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NKlahadore!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Just leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away, Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya, listen to me.\NI was devoted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,For so very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I endured it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I quietly suffered so that\Ntoday I could end your life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and take everything\Nthat I deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NKuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] If he hates\Ngetting hit that much,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,he's about to have\Na really bad day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N"Beat Kuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp the Man's\NTearful Resolve!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE A]\NWhat was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE B]\NIt's sorcery!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE C]\NUh! He's a freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE D]\NA magical freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE E]\NHe sent Captain Kuro flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just leave this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got treasure to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS]\NThe Usopp Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER]\NSay your prayers, butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT]\NTake that! And that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION] Game over,\Nyou lousy, no good pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh! Those kids!\NWhat're they doin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Those rug rats\Nhave a death wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what\Nyou're doing! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER]\NAll right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, we'll let you off\Nwithout any more brutality!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now those stupid kids\Nhave really done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Kuro is gonna be so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Those dummy brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT]\NCaptain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it. You were fighting!\NGosh that is so totally awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought there were no\Nsecrets between us pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That right! We're supposed to\Ntell each other everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, this is important!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys gotta get\Noutta here! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to stay\Nand fight with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Usopp Pirates will be\Nshamed if we run in fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL wheezing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NYou idiots! Don't scream, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,--[thud]\N--[KAYA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS]\NCaptain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NThat hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite a strange technique\Nyou've developed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have powers from\Neating the Devil Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] Yep.\NI'm a rubber man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES whimpering, yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE D]\NAh! He ate the Devil Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE E]\NThat guy's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE F] Those Devil\NFruit people are real!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE G]\NHe's got rubber arms of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It all makes perfect sense now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't just hallucinate his\Narms stretching out like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NJango!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh! Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can handle the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You take care of Miss\NKaya like we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Have her write her\Nbutler into her will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,they're an eyesore.\NEliminate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NStop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna get to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll have to make\Nit through me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NButchie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE]\NCat-tastrophe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NNo. Stay away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No. No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS]\NYes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NI need you to listen carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. We're not running!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not after they did this to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NWe will avenge you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect... Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] Do as I say.\NDon't argue with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm giving you the\Nmost important task
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,there is right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's absolutely critical\Nthat you succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Take Kaya, and get\Naway from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You must keep her safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the reason we\Nwanted to be pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To protect what's dear to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So do as I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go. That's a direct order.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL]\NYes! Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT]\NKaya, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NThis way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER]\NC'mon, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] He's sure got\Na way with words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He made running\Naway sound brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT] I know these woods\Nlike the back of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Jango.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Sorry, I was gawking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Those fools. Do they really\Nthink that they can escape me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,--[thud]\N--[JANGO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO growls] Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a priority right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] Their attempt\Nat escape is futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We know all too well\Nhow weak Kaya is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way they can\Npossibly escape Jango.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, i you want to\Nhelp her, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But first, you'll have to get\Noff this hill alive. Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NButchie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] I guess losing to me once\Nwasn't enough for you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to get outta my way,\Nyou drooling tub of lard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[bang]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] That is the\Nsound of destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Jango's probably tearing\Nthe place apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. See for yourself\Nif you can get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Heartless bastard! Don't you\Neven have a shred of pity?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You lived with that\Ngirl for three years!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NNo. I've told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya is nothing more than a pawn\Nin the game I intend to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When she's dead, then\NI'll be grateful to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NDamn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NThis guy is hopelessly evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] We should put\Nhim out of his misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp! Go find the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, we'll\Ntake care of this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NAh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Very impressive.\NYou can still move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NShut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You betrayed the villager's\Ntrust. Not to mention
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you planned to take the life\Nof a sweet young girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last time\Nyou ever get your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts... It hurts\Nso bad, I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NYou really are a riot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So I betrayed them, you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please! Grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all part of the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A village liar who plays\Npirates with the local kids
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,has no place talking\Nlike a real pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay on the ground there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO] Hah. Even if you\Ndid somehow catch up to Jango,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd end your life\Nin the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying there is\Nwhat's best for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NI don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care that I'm weak.\NI'll protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Captain of\Nthe Usopp Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A brave warrior of the sea who\Nfights for what he holds dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I will protect everyone in\Nthe village if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,On my word, you will never\Nset foot in that village!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE H]\NWhat's his deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE I]\NHe's yellin' about something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE J]\NCheck it out he's crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NLuffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and Usopp are gonna\Nchase down that hypno freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NNo. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be a whole lot faster\Nif I was going by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know those woods,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so if we're gonna catch up to\Nthem, I'm gonna need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it you two. Where\Ndo you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who gave you permission\Nto go anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NI did!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp! Zoro! Get goin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHave another!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NGum-Gum!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NMan, he disappeared again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NThe others got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the most\Nimportant thing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] Before I kill you,\NI feel compelled to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:15:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is an outsider like you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,butting into this\Nvillages' business for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] Because there's\Na man in this village
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that I don't wanna let die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] Simple enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay with that\Nbeing the reason that you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! But I'm not gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NGum-Gum Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is quite boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You cocky jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOwww.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He nicked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro laid him out flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotta good that\NDevil Fruit did him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's Captain\NKuro for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.11,0:17:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up. Don't call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NYou still don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools. This whole\Nplan was devised,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so that I may be rid of that\Nname once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Concocting plans everyday\Nfor a bunch of barbarians
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,who care only about\Nhavoc and mayhem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Relentlessly attacked\Nby government dogs
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and bounty hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sick and tired\Nof that entire cursed life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[explosion]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NThe Navy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the third\Ntime this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, can you really blame them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one of the\Nmost famous pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,sailing the seas right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Kuro is a superstar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NYou're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My infamy is what\Ndraws them to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm going to\Ngive up being Captain Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[explosion]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, wouldn't that be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Except... the Marines\Nwon't stop their pursuit
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,until Captain Kuro is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[explosion]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NI am going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem that the\Ntumultuous life of a pirate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,just isn't for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NYou can't quit, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the ship's captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NYou can be captain now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have finally grown\Nweary of this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over. I'm killing\Nmyself for all to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! Captain Kuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NHow many vessels are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,One! Just one this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do, Captain?!\NShould we man the cannons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We could blast\Nthem to splinters!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] Lower a small\Nboat into the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:18:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE S]\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:18:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NA boat! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE S]\NVice Captain Jango!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Kuro just--!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NYeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE O]\N"Yeah, I know"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous for him\Nto go there by himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE S] Don't tell me\Nhe's turning himself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE R]\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE G]\NThe cannon fire stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE H]\NWhat's goin' on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE I]\NThis is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NPrepare to board the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE T]\NBut... sir! Shouldn't we--?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask for your\Nopinion. That's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE T]\NYes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE R]\NBetter get ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO] I see.\NSo that's why you--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,--[PIRATE H] On three!\N--[PIRATES yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You there! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Yes, sir! What is it, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye. It was nice\Nknowing you, sailor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE T]\NThe Marines.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE V]\NThey've been wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NNow then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NLet's begin this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, pull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was kind enough to let\Nyou and you alone survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just... do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not kneeling to you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish me off and\Nget it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:21:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,--[thud]\N--[MORGAN groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can still howl this\Nmuch with a shattered jaw,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you should do fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the greatest\Nday of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the day you\Ncaptured Captain Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be ever\Nso grateful to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm giving you, the\Nhead of Captain Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NYour name is Captain Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name is Captain Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This atrocity was your doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,One. Two. Jango!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Captain Kuro.\NThis atrocity was my doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NAnd you are the brave Marine
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,who caught the\Ninfamous Captain Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Return to base and see\Nthat he gets executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,One. Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Jango!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the brave Marine who caught\Nthe infamous Captain Kuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE W] You're doing\Nit again, Vice Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NPerfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When my double gets executed,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Kuro will\Ndisappear from the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.29,0:22:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and I will live\Nthe life I deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.05,0:22:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NAnd when my plan succeeds today,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.13,0:22:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,after three years of planning,\Nrevising, and waiting;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,my goal will be achieved\Nin its entirety.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wealth and peace of mind\Nwill finally be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.81,0:22:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand now, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.98,0:22:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not allow\Nthis perfect plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,years in the making, to fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My plan will not be disrupted\Nby an urchin like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.99,0:22:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem that you can do\Na lot more than just stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.12,0:22:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NThat's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been toughening\Nmyself up to be a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what?\NDon't want a reputation?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.59,0:22:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then don't be a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.89,0:23:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just greedy, Kuro.\NBut I have ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.66,0:23:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.28,0:23:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.17,0:23:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.02,0:23:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.65,0:23:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.95,0:23:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.79,0:24:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.05,0:24:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.92,0:24:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.27,0:24:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NI'm worried guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.23,0:24:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Kaya and\Nthe others got away?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.02,0:24:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NRelax. Those three are with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.27,0:24:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,she should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.23,0:24:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NOh, yeah? So she won't get lost
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.03,0:24:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,like someone else I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.24,0:24:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NAre you talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.32,0:24:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWho else is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.24,0:24:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NCan it, jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.41,0:24:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro, you're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.61,0:24:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How much time did you spend lost\Nwhile you were bounty hunting?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.20,0:24:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NOh yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.49,0:24:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.37,0:24:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Protect Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.75,0:24:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Usopp Pirates'\NGreat Efforts!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.12,0:24:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

